                        h2.title EVHC (1)
                        p.txt Every Industry is digitalizing, from hailing a taxi to accessing healthcare provider information. Automotive is no different, with customer expectation and behavior driving the need for change. Electronic Vehicle Health Checks (EVHC) enable you to provide a paperless and transparent experience for both customers and service reception team - ensuring the handover and walk around inspection process is kept to a minimum for a better customer experience and a heightened opportunity for upselling wear & tear parts.



