                        h2.title Challenge
                        p.txt Paper-based walk arounds take a long time to perform. Once the customer has signed, the service advisor will have to key the notes back into the DMS. This creates double the work and allows the Service Advisor to skip OEM or Dealer standard processes, potentially leaving the dealership exposed. On top of the extra work and risk of non-compliance, customers also have a worsened experience as they must spend time waiting as the Advisor refers back to the DMS for information. 


