                        h2.title Solution
                        p.txt Getac Automotive gives workshops the ability to perform easy, integrated and paperless EVHCs. 
                        ol.list
                            li <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> 100% Vehicle Inspections – The Getac EVHC platform mandates that all checks are carried out in accordance with OEM standards, delivering customer peace of mind and more revenue opportunities for the dealer. 
                            li <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Quick Intuitive User Interface – Getac's EVHC platform streamlines the whole process, allowing time estimates and accurate handover times to be generated for a quick decisions. 
